Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回舵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鱼雷正在冲向施佩伯爵号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和鱼雷齐头冲锋
