Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么不改变航向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小代 准备下一轮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}报告受损情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三号炮受损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二号炮中弹 还能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发动机随时可以开足全速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是夹叉射击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小铃 回避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有鱼雷 已穿过施佩伯爵号舰底
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然没有回避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样根本无法瞄准那个弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明瞄得那么准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然我不想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样接舷夺舰的计划根本没法实行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能重新考虑一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小咪 不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但只要正中一炮 这艘小船就会被打个粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能再让大家犯险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我们以前成功过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 可以试试跳艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}的确 机动性强的小型跳艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以轻易躲开炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果被至近弹掀翻了的话 就只能放弃整个作战计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么办 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本舰此后的指挥工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就全权交给你了 宗谷真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突击班 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们必须吸引施佩伯爵号的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}离预计突击时间还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小聪 看我的信号开始突击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轮到咱上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向施佩伯爵号靠近200
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}4 3…准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发现舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真准时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}继续吸引施佩伯爵号的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 对方的副炮直瞄开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪里被打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷达室一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一鱼雷发射管未受创
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第二鱼雷发射管一切平安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 是射击指挥仪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}射击指挥仪 你们还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小笠原 没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武田 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日置 没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能再让大家冒险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 你一定要拿下施佩伯爵号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最大战速 沿最短路线离开对方的射程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}离开对方射程需要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保持最大战速离开主炮射程需要30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副炮则需要20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}诶 还要30分钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第四运用类仓库进水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别以为你们能打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知开打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.64,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.4\fs32\bord2\pos(640,616)\fnTimes New Roman\b1}Wunderbar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 进了这么多水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟啦 百百
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她不在啊 只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁来帮帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炮术科的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帮你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正指挥仪也给打坏了 没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赶紧修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没错 有什么需要尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把这里堵上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家快点开到射程之外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么多水柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 能想个办法吗 干扰一下对方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船已经交给小白她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们要为突击班的意外情况做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴风号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白 拜托你了 保护好大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你还没好吗 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}湿度超过90%了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}通风机是不是停了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}气温超过40度了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还要全速前进吗 外边现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再坚持一会 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宗谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在是我在指挥 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 得令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们再坚持一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 这是人家的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}万里小路流{\fnDFGMaruMoji-W9}薙{\r\blur5}刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被打中的话可是很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兵因敌而制胜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五十六
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}距离施佩伯爵号11海里 离开她们副炮的射程了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还没好吗 还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10分钟后将离开她们的主炮射程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这上面就是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不会放你们过去的 真知知就由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.84,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.4\fs32\bord2\pos(640,616)\fnTimes New Roman\b1}Mein Kapitän
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:38.89,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.4\fs32\bord2\pos(640,616)\fnTimes New Roman\b1}Entschuldigung, ich bin zu spät
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知 我帮上你忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第十只了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大功十件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美波同学 抗体都接种完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打完这针就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明乃 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小咪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}介绍一下 她就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是舰长西娅·克莱采 事情我都听她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是晴风号舰长岬明乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副舰长 宗谷真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们所有人都没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们准备回希亚德勒基地补给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那小咪也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 当然会和我们一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保险起见回去以后接受一下精密体检吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}饭做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是三文鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.96,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.4\fs32\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\pos(664,616)\b1}Lachsfilet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还可以叫寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们也帮了手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还放了马铃薯丸和鲱鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寿司 刺身 还有过劳死？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:30.25,Remark,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}注：正确的叫法很可能是Kluski。\N又及，过劳死这个单词的日文读法及其意义被直接挪用到了英语圈及德语圈。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最后那个说错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是大锅菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 舰长 还可以叫关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}关东煮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 说句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}经过我们不断地努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终于光复了舰船 恢复了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这个值得庆祝的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有请晴风号的舰长带头干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么 各位 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.94,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.4\fs32\bord2\pos(640,616)\fnTimes New Roman\b1}Prost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来 舰长 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是香肠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是我们船上特制的香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早就想吃这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}味道真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}舰长 老夫一直代你保管着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帮我戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这位舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过你们的船好像受损很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这都是拜谁所赐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过 技术还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然离打败我们还差那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要和我们一起回希亚德勒维修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我们接到命令准备和明石号会合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗 那么就在此别过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}酒杯我这就还你 以后别把我当晴风号的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要我回 我也不回了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们也一样 一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.33,Default UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}{\fs32\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\pos(640,616)\b1}Gute reise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这笔生意还是亏本了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我现在已经一穷二白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:06.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,531.333)}多灾多难的明娜作战！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:13.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:19.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}言葉よりも優しく　背中を押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:25.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}そう　私と君のripple effect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:42.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}果てなく向かってくる波は険しいばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:48.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}航路はどうしよう　君と選ぶ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.73,0:22:55.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}微笑み忘れたら　私が笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:03.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}涙弾けたあとは　強さが水面に広がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:12.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:16.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}言葉よりも優しく波打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:20.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}晴れた空とあの風と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:26.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰かのそばで　夢を描くのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その誰かが私でありたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:35.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\3c&HD7C392&\c&HFAF7EF&}きっと春が待ってくれてるから
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,【EDCN】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:13.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}青色七洋 今天也环绕着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:19.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}我会比话语还要温柔 轻轻地推着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:25.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFAE5D3&\3c&H6F3B1B&\blur2}是啊 这就是你和我之间的涟漪效应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:42.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}面前的惊涛骇浪 一浪卷来一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:48.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我们选择的航路 就是我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.73,0:22:55.49,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}如果你忘记了微笑 我会笑给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:03.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H5064CE&\blur2}流过眼泪之后 让坚强随波布散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:12.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}青色七洋 今天也环绕着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:16.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}比话语还要温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:20.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}是这片晴空和习习凉风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:26.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果你希望有人能陪你一起描绘梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我希望我就是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:35.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\3c&HD7C392&\c&HFAF7EF&}要相信春天正在等待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事情还算顺利 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是晴风号却受了这么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:24:00.00,Post_End,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,570)}下集老夫也要看片！
